org.perfcake.reporting

Class MeasurementUnit

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.perfcake.reporting.MeasurementUnit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class MeasurementUnit
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A result of the smallest measurement unit - an iteration. One should obtain a new instance of a MeasurementUnit using ReportManager.newMeasurementUnit().
    Author:
    Martin Večeřa
    See Also:
